      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six. The powertrain is in excellent mechanical health, featuring a serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural integrity under high torque loads. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential, ensuring exceptional traction out of corners. The chassis remains sharp with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a well-sorted suspension setup. While it displays minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, its mechanical performance is precise, offering the linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback these icons are known for.",
